<code>react-relay</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-24T04:00:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Starter Kits</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mhart/simple-relay-starter\">Simple Relay Starter</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mhart/simple-relay-starter\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">158</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":158,\"repo\":\"mhart/simple-relay-starter\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A Browserify version of the <a href=\"https://github.com/relayjs/relay-starter-kit\">Relay Starter Kit</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/relayjs/relay-starter-kit\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1032,\"repo\":\"relayjs/relay-starter-kit\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-24T03:57:22.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries &#x26; Packages</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/relay-tools/relay-local-schema\"><code>relay-local-schema</code></a> - Use a local schema; no need for a remote GraphQL server.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-24T03:51:00.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries &#x26; Packages</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/4Catalyzer/relay-decorators\"><code>relay-decorator</code></a> - Simply syntax for Relay containers with ES7 decorators (<code>@</code> syntax)</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-24T03:49:00.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries &#x26; Packages</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/recompose-relay\"><code>recompose-relay</code></a> - Ease composition of Relay containers by currying and providing the component after the container.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-24T03:49:00.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://auth0.com/blog/2015/10/06/getting-started-with-relay/\">Getting Started with Relay</a> - One of the few detailed walk throughs of hand-on Relay.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T08:09:34.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Documentation</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/relay/docs/getting-started.html#content\">Official Docs</a> - Official Relay documentation.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:50:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tutorials</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@clayallsopp/relay-101-building-a-hacker-news-client-bb8b2bdc76e6#.1i64q1pf9\">Relay 101: Building A Hacker News Client</a> - A complete workable example.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@clayallsopp/relay-102-mutations-d8b471a4730e#.i9vuv3vxl\">Relay 102: Mutations</a> - A follow up to \"Relay 101\" concentrating on mutations.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:50:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Overviews</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.sitepoint.com/react-data-fetching-with-relay/\">React Data Fetching with Relay</a> - Clear conceptual overview of Relay's moving parts and magic.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:50:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Libraries &#x26; Packages</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/relay-tools/react-router-relay\"><code>react-router-relay</code></a> - <code>react-router</code> bindings for Relay. Greatly simplifies many local state UI uses cases.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/@cpojer/relay-and-routing-36b5439bad9#.h91614i65\">Relay and Routing</a> - A well-articulated walk through of <code>react-router-relay</code>, and the problems that it solves.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/relay-nested-routes\"><code>relay-nested-routes</code></a> - Generate nested routes that reflect nested data. Helpful for managing deep data.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/denvned/isomorphic-relay-router\"><code>isomorphic-relay-router</code></a> - Server side rendering support for <code>react-router-relay</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:50:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tooling</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/graphql/graphiql\">GraphiQL</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/graphql/graphiql\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":12103,\"repo\":\"graphql/graphiql\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A library to introspect GraphQL, test queries and mutations.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/skevy/graphiql-app\">GraphiQL App</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/skevy/graphiql-app\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.6k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2622,\"repo\":\"skevy/graphiql-app\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A standalone app for viewing GraphQL, introspection docs, and testing queries/mutations. Invaluable for debugging your Relay app.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:50:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Starter Kits</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/relayjs/relay-starter-kit\">Relay Starter Kit</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/relayjs/relay-starter-kit\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1032,\"repo\":\"relayjs/relay-starter-kit\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - An app that it already set up with a basic setup. Just clone and tweak to suit your needs!</li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:50:49.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Lists of Lists</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://quip.com/oLxzA1gTsJsE\">Relay and GraphQL Introduction Materials</a></li>","updatedAt":"2015-12-08T07:22:43.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/enaqx/awesome-react","repo":"enaqx/awesome-react"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/glauberfc/awesome-react-hooks","repo":"glauberfc/awesome-react-hooks"}},"pageContext":{"repo":"expede/awesome-relay","id":"awesomes/github.com/expede/awesome-relay","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/enaqx/awesome-react","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/glauberfc/awesome-react-hooks"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","3289010534"]}